dialog.body: Hello, thank you for contacting Old Stone Auto Insurance. My name is Vincent Sanchez. May I have your name, please?
Hello, Vincent. My name is Kimberly Rodriguez.
Nice to meet you, Kimberly. How are you doing today?
I'm doing well, thank you for asking.
Great to hear! To assist you further, could you kindly provide your policy number and date of birth for verification purposes?
Of course. My policy number is one two three four five and my date of birth is January fifth, nineteeneightyseven.
Thank you for that information. Is there anything specific you need help with regarding your policy today, Kimberly?
I would like to inquire about adding a new vehicle to my policy.
I can certainly assist you with that request. Please provide me with the make, model, and year of the vehicle you wish to add.
Thank you for your time, Kimberly. If you have any more questions, don't hesitate to reach out. Have a wonderful day!
